title: Tattoos and Diamonds - Chippa Wilson #LIVEARNETTE
description: Chippa Wilson is known for his innovative surf style, but something he's equally proud of is the ink that adorns his skin. In this Episode of the #LIVEARNETTE series, Chippa speaks about his tattoos and the meanings behind them.
